{"tid":754164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人民日報：中美貿易戰美國將自食惡果","createTime":"2018-07-24T07:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-26T06:47:23.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"634e80c69cebf114674d58340b9718b04cd7ed47","tid":754164,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:43:05.000Z","msg":"內地官方《人民日報》就中美貿易戰發表評論文章，指挑起中美貿易戰，美國必將自食惡果。文章批評，貿易戰已動搖美國的國家信譽，指中美高級別經貿團隊經過四輪磋商，發表不打貿易戰的聯合聲明，但美方數天後就食言，批評美國出爾反爾、言而無信。文章又指，貿易戰損害美國的經濟利益，關稅將會轉嫁到消費者，美國在華企業利益受到衝擊，亦會打爛大量美國民眾的飯碗，同時傷及美國的國際形象，損害全球供應鏈，破壞多邊貿易體制，衝擊美國的軟實力。<br />\n<br />\n文章指出，中國在這場貿易戰中亦會遭受損失，但不得不回應，需要給美國迎頭痛擊，讓美國痛定思痛，真正認識到打貿易戰對美國、別國和世界都是災難，從而懸崖勒馬，迷途知返。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1020487&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1020487%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2FrI7eD%2F6V29ZkNZAC5nNgDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=0a70adb8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1020487&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"4f9dbd013996c150b12ae8340658e8c9c1fae3ee","tid":754164,"uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T07:45:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://big5.gov.cn/gate/big5/www.gov.cn/zhengce/site1/20151116/74541447647475404.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbig5.gov.cn%2Fgate%2Fbig5%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fzhengce%2Fsite1%2F20151116%2F74541447647475404.jpg&h=cd3bd98b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adb8e2040c263ca6fbef192f56f49d7e837555ae","tid":754164,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T09:59:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8955691c590c643cee99303ccea717da3e30b81c","tid":754164,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-24T10:01:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},